{"TopicId":178700,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"Working(-ish) rocket chess.","CreatedByName":"Kerbalstar","CreatedById":154159,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-03T03:20:36Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Kerbalstar","CreatedById":154159,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-03T03:20:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nInspired by this thread below, I decided to create a working chess board in KSP.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed8430367661\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/178454-need-advice-on-chess-pieces/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:227px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow \u0022working\u0022 is a bit over-zealous, but it mostly\u003Csup\u003E tm\u00A0\u003C/sup\u003Eworks. I\u0027ve managed to move a pawn one square forward so far. Some notes:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nYou need to cheat it (Mod-F12) to orbit, within a few seconds, or it shakes itself apart.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nYou should probably turn on infinite\u00A0fuel and EC, or the probes may run out of electric charge, and your moves will be limited to the (limited) fuel in the tanks on the pieces.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nTo control the knights, queens, and kings, (bum, bum, bum \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0), you need to put a Kerbal in the command seat. To do this, put some command pods on the bottom, or install TakeCommandContinued by \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/129964-linuxgurugamer/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022129964\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/129964-linuxgurugamer/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@linuxgurugamer\u003C/a\u003E , or wait for KSP 1.5\u003C/span\u003E when this warning will be rendered null and void.\u00A0\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nWithout further ado, some pics, and links for some clicks! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022rpAXqcM.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022682\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/rpAXqcM.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022eGlQ9S0.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022682\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/eGlQ9S0.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022bJmnC80.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022682\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/bJmnC80.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022BXo1HeW.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022682\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/BXo1HeW.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022wCjaCr0.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022682\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/wCjaCr0.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cdiv title=\u0022Protected by Grammarly\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDownload link:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalx.com/Kerbalstar/Chess-board\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://kerbalx.com/Kerbalstar/Chess-board\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klond","CreatedById":38787,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-14T00:15:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0Looks nice\u00A0and square and straight and level.\u00A0 I think moving pieces while in orbit is probably the best way to do it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0That said\u00A0I wanna make a piece mover so I don\u0027t have to leave the runway.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0Having expansion parts really makes the board look proper.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbalstar","CreatedById":154159,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-14T00:34:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223467305\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022178700\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221539476131\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002238787\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022klond\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 minutes ago, klond said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0Looks nice\u00A0and square and straight and level.\u00A0 I think moving pieces while in orbit is probably the best way to do it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0That said\u00A0I wanna make a piece mover so I don\u0027t have to leave the runway.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0Having expansion parts really makes the board look proper.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks! It only works in space. That would be cool. Remember that you can always F12 it to orbit!\u00A0Thanks!\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}